title: EYL #164 DJ Khaled on Social Media Marketing, Being a Mogul, Ghost Kitchens, & More
itunes:title: EYL #164 DJ Khaled on Social Media Marketing, Being a Mogul, Ghost Kitchens, & More
description:
On episode #164 we sat down with the legendary DJ Khaled. He spoke about his journey in music, becoming an entrepreneur, mastering social media, his keys to marketing and more. This episode was a collaboration with Untied Masters, and was sponsored by Ally. 


This conversation was took place live at EYL & United Masters Art Basel Activation “Earn Your Masters”. #djkhaled #business #music
